# Surfraw for ArchLinux
https://ostechnix.com/surfraw-commandline-interface-popular-search-engines-100-websites/

## Install Surfraw
sudo pacman -Syyu surfraw

## Configure Surfraw
mkdir ~/.config/surfraw/

sudo vi ~/.config/surfraw/conf
SURFRAW_graphical_browser=/usr/bin/chromium
SURFRAW_text_browser=/usr/bin/lynx
SURFRAW_graphical=yes

## Surfraw elvi`s
surfraw -elvi

## Search with surfraw
surfraw google linux
